title: "TDF Benchmark Lab: Controlled ΛCDM/GR Recovery and Stress Tests for the Time Delay Field Framework"
version: 0.1.0
date-released: 2026-05-16
authors:
  - family-names: Masarrat
    given-names: Bahman
