abstract: >
  Reproducible benchmark and calibration diagnostics for the Time Delay Field (TDF)
  v0.8.1 framework. Provides controlled ΛCDM/GR recovery tests and stress regimes
  using synthetic teachers only. Does not constitute observational validation.
